  "title": "feat: rename packages",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR removes the following packages from the monorepo:\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n- react-instantsearch-dom\r\n- react-instantsearch-dom-maps\r\n- react-instantsearch-native\r\n\r\nIt then renames the packages in this fashion:\r\n- react-instantsearch-hooks-web → react-instantsearch\r\n- react-instantsearch-hooks → react-instantsearch-core\r\n- react-instantsearch-hooks-router-nextjs → react-instantsearch-router-nextjs\r\n- react-instantsearch-hooks-server → all files included in react-instantsearch-core/server\r\n\r\nMisc:\r\n- react examples are replaced with those from react-hooks\r\n- configuration and ci is updated\r\n\r\n\r\nFX-2338\r\n\r\n> **Note**  \r\n> It will probably be easier to review commit by commit, and ignore the first one (\"move packages\") as it just shuffles around a bunch of files.\r\n",
